WiFiAgent(8)                System Manager's Manual               WiFiAgent(8)

NAME
     WiFiAgent – Wi-Fi User agent.

DESCRIPTION
     WiFiAgent is the User Agent to perform Wi-Fi tasks on behalf of
     airportd(8).  This must not be invoked directly.

SEE ALSO
     airportd(8)

